resolveVersionedResource

public static JUFormBinding resolveVersionedResource(VersionDef version,
                                                     java.lang.String resName)
Finds the resource definition in a given version. If there is no mapping entry for the given resource name in the given version, this method will search in previous versions until a matching entry is found.

Parameters:
version - the requested version
resName - the name of the resource definition to retrieve
Returns:
the requested resource definition, or null if no matching entry is found.

getAvailableResources

public static java.util.Collection<java.lang.String> getAvailableResources(VersionDef requestVersion)
Gets all the resources available for the specified version.

Parameters:
requestVersion - the requested version
Returns:
the unqualified resource name (without the version prefix) for all resources available in the requested version.
